rows.label: qst200233_msg0001
rows.name:
You're searching for Harghal, Mo-mo?
I haven't seen her since former
Chairman Bahn disappeared, mo.

rows.label: qst200233_msg0005
rows.name:
If you want to know about Harghal, you
should try visiting a girl named Couche
who works at Harapekko Canteen, mo.

rows.label: qst200233_msg0007
rows.name:
That girl did the same work and
was Harghal's close friend, so I
think she knows the details, mo.
